      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652396210_1937630743505233_2519231331305288601_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MjY0OTE3ODc4MzEzMjk4MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=__1bsnXGe5AQ7kNvwHITjC8&amp;_nc_oc=AdrDiMa_0OQMQz0T1eoVtyBaxZkPpaVYG0NVgqjgflo_sBdnczpZizeSWKEcfhycQcw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=b_5nLtz4eH38iGKzPLNMew&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwkHWhEVU9wGhiLvPoLUgVQ0EVZuweGufOAXI3ldqpZaw&amp;oe=69C9084C" alt="Instagram billede fra @jacob_fabricius" /></p><p><strong>@jacob_fabricius</strong></p><p>DemonLovers Inc., Under the Database, 2026, Video (color, sound), 11‘02’’<br/>
<br/>
DemonLovers Inc. @daemonlovers is a collaborative project by Dayana Matasheva and Edson Niebla based in New York City. The duo works primarily with video and installation, occasionally producing painting, sculpture, and performance. They have been commissioned to create online content as a pre-opening for the exhibition Setting the Tone of The Exhibition (outside-in) at Inside-Out Art Museum, Beijing. @jacob_fabricius</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652396210_1937630743505233_2519231331305288601_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MjY0OTE3ODc4MzEzMjk4MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=__1bsnXGe5AQ7kNvwHITjC8&amp;_nc_oc=AdrDiMa_0OQMQz0T1eoVtyBaxZkPpaVYG0NVgqjgflo_sBdnczpZizeSWKEcfhycQcw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=b_5nLtz4eH38iGKzPLNMew&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwkHWhEVU9wGhiLvPoLUgVQ0EVZuweGufOAXI3ldqpZaw&amp;oe=69C9084C" alt="Instagram billede fra @jacob_fabricius" /></p><p><strong>@jacob_fabricius</strong></p><p>DemonLovers Inc., Under the Database, 2026, Video (color, sound), 11‘02’’<br/>
<br/>
DemonLovers Inc. @daemonlovers is a collaborative project by Dayana Matasheva and Edson Niebla based in New York City. The duo works primarily with video and installation, occasionally producing painting, sculpture, and performance. They have been commissioned to create online content as a pre-opening for the exhibition Setting the Tone of The Exhibition (outside-in) at Inside-Out Art Museum, Beijing. @jacob_fabricius</p>]]></content:encoded>
